descriptionHtml:
[center][b][u]Description
[/u][/b]
A pair of RaceMenu presets for Saber Artorias and Sakura Saber by Type-Moon. Figured I would share them for anyone interested. 

Sakura Saber has yellow eyes and a more pinkish hair color. Artorias is full blonde with green eyes. 



[u]Mods Used[/u]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]Dimonized UNP Body[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu 3.X (duh)[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56056/?]Mikan Eyes [/url]

RadioReggae's Hair (Steam Workshop) 

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Eyebrows [/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58989]Citrus Heads HD (Standalone!) [/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602]Fair Skin Complexion[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/689]Detailed Lips [/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665]Better Makeup SKSE 



[/url][b][u]Instructions[/u][/b]

Simply drag and drop the "SKSE" folder into your data folder or use the mod manager of your choice. 


[u][b]ENB Preset Used

[/b][/u][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71860/?]Evok ENB[/url]
